1. *Radu* sam se posvetio poslu. (I am devoted to work.)
2. Ovo je posao koji zahteva dosta *rada*. (This is a job that requires a lot of work.)
3. On je dobar u *radu* sa ljudima. (He is good at working with people.)
4. *Radu* se ne sme nikad odreći. (Work should never be abandoned.)
5. *Radu* nema kraja. (There is no end to work.)
6. Oni rade *radove* na putu. (They are doing construction work on the road.)
7. *Radovi* na zgradi su gotovi. (The building works are finished.)
8. Uživam u *radu* u bašti. (I enjoy working in the garden.)
9. Oni *rade* na novom projektu. (They are working on a new project.)
10. *Radiš* dobro, nastavi tako. (You are doing well, keep it up.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "radu" can have several different meanings depending on the context. It can mean "work", "labor", "job", "toil", "occupation", or "task". It can also be used in different forms such as "rad", "radovi", "radi", and "radiš".